  "body": "<p>Woohoo! Remember when I talked about Cut &amp; Paste a couple months ago in this blog post? Well, Two Peas in a Bucket and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=cut%20%26%20paste&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D60077%2F366066%2D8%2Dpage%2Dsticker%2FDetail\">Simon Says Stamp</a> both have the newest collection with American Crafts in store now! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/06be6c5a30178288.jpg?v=1782528579\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Supplies: <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144205-infatuation-12x12-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-paper/\">Infatuation paper</a> - also available in the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144228-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-12x12-paper-pad/\">12 x 12 paper pad </a>| <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144237-begonia-cut-outs-rubber-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-thickers/\">Rubber Thickers in Begonia</a> | <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144238-cut-out-accents-printed-chipboard-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-thickers/\">Cut Out Accents</a> | <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144248-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-die-cut-shapes/\">Bits die cut shapes</a> | <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/144240-harper-cut-paste-amy-tangerine-tiny-alpha-transparent-stickers/\">Harper mini alpha stickers</a> | <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=die%20cut%20tags&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D61003%2F366069%2Ddie%2Dcut%2Dtags%2FDetail\">Bits die cut tags</a> (sold out but you can click Notify Me)</p><p>Check out all the Cut &amp; Paste items online at Two Peas in a Bucket and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=cut%20%26%20paste&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D60077%2F366066%2D8%2Dpage%2Dsticker%2FDetail\">Simon Says Stamp</a> - and ask your local retailers when they will be arriving. Can't wait to see what you create! </p>"
